\varphi(x)=\sum_{k\ge 1}\frac{x_k}{2^k}=\sum_{k=1}^n\frac{b_k}{2^k}+\sum_{k>n}\frac{x_k}{2^k}=\frac{m}{2^n}+\sum_{k>n}\frac{x_k}{2^k}\;,
